      <p>Hipsell may amend, revise or modify this Privacy Policy in whole or in part at any time and from time to time and post such new policy on its website at www.hipsell.com.  Your continued use of the Service following the posting of any such amended, revised or modified Privacy Policy constitutes your acceptance of the current version of this Privacy Policy.</p>
      <p>Effective August 11, 2011</p>
    </div>
  '''
